<div class="card mb-3 p-4 border-0">
  <div class="row intro">
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <img src="<%= asset_pack_path 'media/images/xianqin.jpeg'%>" class="img-thumbnail">
    </div>
    <div class="col">
      <div class="card-body pt-1">
        <h4 class="category card-title mx-0 mt-0">百家争鸣</h4>
        <div class="d-flex mb-2">
          <blockquote class="flex-grow-1 blockquote mb-0">
            <p class="mb-2">人生天地之间，若白驹过隙，忽然而已。</p>
            <footer class="blockquote-footer float-right">庄子</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="d-flex mb-2">
          <blockquote class="flex-grow-1 blockquote mb-0">
            <p class="mb-2">审其所好恶，则其长短可知也。</p>
            <footer class="blockquote-footer float-right">管子</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="d-flex mb-2">
          <blockquote class="flex-grow-1 blockquote mb-0">
            <p class="mb-2">知者乐水，仁者乐山； 知者动，仁者静； 知者乐，仁者寿。</p>
            <footer class="blockquote-footer float-right">孔子</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="d-flex mb-2">
          <blockquote class="flex-grow-1 blockquote mb-0">
            <p class="mb-2">凡学之不勤，必其志之未笃也。</p>
            <footer class="blockquote-footer float-right">列子</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>